29:["$","p",null,{"className":"pb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed","style":{"color":"#666666"},"children":"Yes. Our taping machines are designed to work with standard 48mm or 72mm wide BOPP tape rolls on a 76mm core — the same specification as the tape rolls we supply. This ensures consistent compatibility between your machine and tape."}]
